info.name: GMail Nice Pack
info.description:
Compilation Package of Best Gmail Styles
Outlook.com style for Gmail. Minimalist, metro-like appearance for Gmail and Google Calendar + Mailbox Icons Sidebar + Easy Access Colored Buttons + Small Attachment Icons
info.additionalInfo:
Based on :

  • - Pimp.my.Gmail Sidebar (by Kilroy)
  • - Gmail Easy Access Colored Buttons (by Stevesigma)
  • - Gmail *2* small attachment icons (by Moktoipas)
